{"data":[{"name":"91:1","price":"Demi matahari dan cahayanya di pagi hari,","arabic":"وَٱلشَّمۡسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6044,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:2","price":"dan bulan apabila mengiringinya,","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6045,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:3","price":"dan siang apabila menampakkannya,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6046,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:4","price":"dan malam apabila menutupinya1580,","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6047,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1580.  Maksudnya malam-malam yang gelap. ","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:5","price":"dan langit serta pembinaannya,","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6048,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:6","price":"dan bumi serta penghamparannya,","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا طَحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6049,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:7","price":"dan jiwa serta penyempurnaannya (ciptaannya),","arabic":"وَنَفۡسٖ وَمَا سَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6050,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:8","price":"maka Allah mengilhamkan kepada jiwa itu (jalan) kefasikan dan ketakwaannya,","arabic":"فَأَلۡهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقۡوَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6051,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:9","price":"sesungguhnya beruntunglah orang yang menyucikan jiwa itu,","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن زَكَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6052,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:10","price":"dan sesungguhnya merugilah orang yang mengotorinya.","arabic":"وَقَدۡ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6053,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:11","price":"(Kaum) Ṡamūd telah mendustakan (rasulnya) karena mereka melampaui batas,","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ بِطَغۡوَىٰهَآ","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6054,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:12","price":"ketika bangkit orang yang paling celaka di antara mereka,","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشۡقَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6055,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:13","price":"lalu rasul Allah (Ṣālīḥ) berkata kepada mereka, (\"Biarkanlah) unta betina Allah dan minumannya\".","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمۡ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقۡيَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6056,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:14","price":"Lalu mereka mendustakannya dan menyembelih unta itu, maka Tuhan mereka membinasakan mereka disebabkan dosa mereka, lalu Allah menyama-ratakan mereka (dengan tanah),","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَعَقَرُوهَا فَدَمۡدَمَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ رَبُّهُم بِذَنۢبِهِمۡ فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6057,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:15","price":"dan Allah tidak takut terhadap akibat tindakan-Nya itu.","arabic":"وَلَا يَخَافُ عُقۡبَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6058,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams","Chapter Ash-Shams","Shams","Surah Shams","Chapter Shams","Ash Shams","Surah Ash Shams","Chapter Ash Shams","Surah 91","Chapter 91","The Sun","الشمس"]}